	Proposed by Juan Manuel Palacios

2008-07-11  Matthias Clasen  <mclasen@redhat.com>

	* gdk-pixbuf-io.c: Use GIO for sniffing image types, except
	on Win32, where GIO doesn't do any sniffing.

