	* io-pnm.c (pnm_read_next_value): Check for overflow.
	(#306394, Morten Welinder)

2005-05-27  Matthias Clasen  <mclasen@redhat.com>

	* io-bmp.c: Accept the 108 byte header of BMP v4.  (#168799)

