	* === Released 2.4.1 ===

2004-04-13  Matthias Clasen  <mclasen@redhat.com>

	* io-ani.c (gdk_pixbuf__ani_image_load_animation): 
	* gdk-pixbuf-io.c (gdk_pixbuf_get_file_info) 
	(_gdk_pixbuf_generic_image_load) 
